pyrikura is a mashup of:

    - a python twisted service that:
        - interfaces with an arduino over a virtual tty
        - captures still images to disk
        - services preview images over a network port
        - processes images from camera

    - a kivy application to browse photos
    - a loose framework of functions that process images and files

all files contained in this directory are copyright leif theden, 2012-2014 and
are licensed under the gplv3.
